Name:		linux-firmware
Version:	@VERSION@
Release:	@REL@%{?dist}
Summary:	Firmware files used by the Linux kernel
# Automatically converted from old format: GPL+ and GPLv2+ and MIT and Redistributable, no modification permitted - review is highly recommended.
